ortant habits","target":"Words I've used to describe important habits","line":17},{"title":"Habit formation provides an evolutionary advantage","target":"Habit formation provides an evolutionary advantage","line":19},{"title":"Habits carry a ton of hidden inertia","target":"Habits carry a ton of hidden inertia","line":20},{"title":"Defining a habit","target":"Defining a habit","line":22},{"title":"Positive Feedback Loop","target":"Positive Feedback Loop","line":26},{"title":"Cobwebs into Cables","target":"Cobwebs into Cables","line":28},{"title":"Newton's Laws of Motion","target":"Newton's Laws of Motion","line":30},{"title":"Natural Selection","target":"Natural Selection","line":32},{"title":"Survival of the Fittest TK","target":"Survival of the Fittest TK","line":34},{"title":"Selfish Gene TK","target":"Selfish Gene TK","line":36},{"title":"Habits MOC","target":"Habits MOC","line":40}],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
